name: Architect Breaks Down 5 Haunted Houses From Scary Films | Architectural Digest - YouTube

content.html: Michael Wyetzner of Michielli + Wyetzner Architects returns to AD, this time breaking down the architectural and design details of haunted houses in five classic films. From the wintery and ominous Overlook Hotel in the ‘The Shining’ to the unnerving suburbia of ‘Get Out,’ Michael highlights all the things you might have missed at these spooky movie locales.
